{"word":"G1607 - ἐκπορεύομαι - ekporeúomai - ek-por-yoo'-om-ahee - Come","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκπορεύομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekporeúomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-por-yoo'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புறப்படு, போ, நீங்கு"},{"paragraph":"to go forth, go out, depart"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G4198 - πορεύομαι - poreúomai - por-yoo'-om-ahee/4198\">G4198</a>; to <i>depart</i>, <i>be discharged</i>, <i>proceed</i>, <i>project:</i> - come (forth, out of), depart, go (forth, out), issue, proceed (out of).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1531/1531\">G1531</a>, <a href=\"#/G1607/1607\">G1607</a>, <a href=\"#/G4198/4198\">G4198</a>"}]}